data.description: As you walk up to this beautiful home you will notice a covered porch with newer pavers, great for relaxing and visiting with friends and neighbors.  Stepping into your home is a generous size great room graced with high end laminate flooring . Your kitchen has natural hard wood cabinets, soft close drawers and closet pantry, a perfect size for all your kitchen gadgets.  The master bedroom is sizable. It can easily fit a king bed and features a walk-in closet and solid wood plantation shutters. The bathroom is updated and modern with tub and recessed shower shelving. There are sliding glass doors leading from your kitchen to your insulated covered outdoor patio.    Here are a NEW features:  Newer IMPACT windows, 2016 roof with 50-year platinum Protection Ltd Lifetime warranty and all new facia, every door replaced including closets, newer hot water heater, water softener, newer garage door, Faux wood blinds in two bedrooms and kitchen, new solid wood blinds in the living room, new vertical blinds on the sliding glass doors.  The exterior of the home was painted a year ago. Just 2.5 miles from the beach and one block from Anona Elementary.   Close to fine dining, hospitals parks and more. Also eligible for AIRBNB
